### Configure Textarea Field Type in Payload CMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/textarea.mdx

This TypeScript snippet demonstrates how to define a Textarea field within a Payload CMS field configuration. It shows setting the 'type' property to 'textarea' to enable the field for longer text input. This configuration is part of a larger Payload 'Field' definition.

```ts
import type { Field } from 'payload'

export const MyTextareaField: Field = {
  // ...
  type: 'textarea', // highlight-line
}
```

