### Override Payload CMS Product Collection Fields (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/ecommerce/plugin.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to extend the default `products` collection in Payload CMS by adding a custom `notes` field of type `textarea`. It utilizes the `productsCollectionOverride` option within the products configuration to access and modify the `defaultCollection` object.

```ts
products: {
  productsCollectionOverride: ({ defaultCollection }) => ({
    ...defaultCollection,
    fields: [
      ...defaultCollection.fields,
      {
        name: 'notes',
        label: 'Notes',
        type: 'textarea'
      }
    ]
  })
}
```

