### Example Payload CMS Collection with UI Field

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/ui.mdx

This example shows a Payload CMS collection configuration that includes a UI field. It specifies custom React components for both the field in the edit view and the cell in the list view. The 'name' and 'type' are required properties for a UI field.

```typescript
import type { CollectionConfig } from 'payload'

export const ExampleCollection: CollectionConfig = {
  slug: 'example-collection',
  fields: [
    {
      name: 'myCustomUIField', // required
      type: 'ui', // required
      admin: {
        components: {
          Field: '/path/to/MyCustomUIField',
          Cell: '/path/to/MyCustomUICell',
        },
      },
    },
  ],
}
```

