### Implement Payload CMS Collapsible Field Section

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Shows a 'collapsible' field that groups 'customCSS' and 'customJS' fields within an expandable/collapsible section in the Payload CMS admin. The label is dynamic, based on `data.title`, and the section is initialized as collapsed.

```ts
import type { CollapsibleField } from 'payload'

const collapsibleField: CollapsibleField = {
  label: ({ data }) => data?.title || 'Advanced Options',
  type: 'collapsible',
  admin: {
    initCollapsed: true,
  },
  fields: [
    { name: 'customCSS', type: 'textarea' },
    { name: 'customJS', type: 'code' },
  ],
}
```

